      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>式微式微，胡不歸？微君之故，胡為乎中露？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Reduced! Reduced!
Why not return?
If it were not for your sake, O prince,
How should we be thus exposed to the dew?</seg>
      </tuv>
